  "about": {
    "title": {
      "zh": "关于",
      "en": "About"
    },
    "desc": {
      "en": "Slackfruit on the slackfruit tree, under the slackfruit tree, you and me.",
      "zh": "摸鱼树上摸鱼果，摸鱼树下你和我"
    },
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "zh": "喜欢看好看的图片，欣赏好看的作品。",
        "en": "I love looking at pretty pictures and appreciating beautiful works."
      },
      {
        "zh": "虽然爱玩很多游戏，但是由于比较懒所以目前只玩崩三、崩铁、终末地了...",
        "en": "Even though I like playing lots of games, I'm kind of lazy, so at the moment I'm only playing Honkai Impact 3rd, Honkai: Star Rail, and Arknights: Endfield..."
      },
      {
        "zh": "喜欢很多番剧和角色，诸如一些少女乐队番、轻百番、异世界题材我大概都蛮喜欢的~",
        "en": "I'm into a lot of anime and characters—stuff like girl band anime, light yuri / CGDCT shows, and isekai, I'm generally a fan of all those~"
      },
      {
        "zh": "不喜欢看恐怖的东西，有点胆小说是...",
        "en": "I don't like scary things; I'm a bit of a scaredy-cat, you could say..."
      },
      {
        "zh": "由于有些晕3D所以也很难去玩一些3D的游戏，诸如第一人称设计、大型3A都玩不太了好可惜...",
        "en": "I also get a little motion sickness from 3D games, so it's hard for me to play 3D titles—like first-person shooters or big AAA games, which is such a shame..."
      },
      {
        "zh": "不过，欢迎与我分享有趣的事情或者美图，虽然我是INFP有些社恐，但我还是会与大家开开心心地交流的！",
        "en": "But still, feel free to share fun things or pretty pictures with me~ Even though I'm an INFP with a bit of social anxiety, I'll still happily chat with everyone!"
      }
    ],
